Comment: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,第57次
Comment: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆外調查開始
Comment: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前進!!
Comment: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在艾連．葉卡位於希干希納區的老家地下室之中
Comment: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,藏著連他自己都不知道的巨人之謎
Comment: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們將以此為目標
Comment: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們新兵在這裡
Comment: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬車的護衛部隊與搜索支援部隊的中間
Comment: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,預備的馬與裝備以及訊息傳達就交給你們了
Comment: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們特別作戰班在這裡
Comment: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,隊伍的中央待命
Comment: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是在這個陣形中最安全的地方
Comment: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,比起搬運物資的馬車還來的輕鬆的待遇
Comment: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她不是奇行種...
Comment: 0,0:00:59.00,0:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,希斯!
Comment: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她具有智慧
Comment: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就跟盔甲和超大型...
Comment: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有艾連一樣
Comment: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是有著巨人身軀的人類
Comment: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,行動的精確度遠超過其他巨人啊!
Comment: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡!
Comment: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太小看...  太過小看她了!
Comment: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然知道要保護後頸?!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死的!
Comment: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經逃不掉了!
Comment: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰!
Comment: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,替那個趕著去投胎的傢伙報仇吧!
Comment: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,停住不動了?!
Comment: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是她! 就是被她殺死的!
Comment: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,右翼的那傢伙在趕著去投胎的路上就掛了
Comment: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,替那個趕著去投胎的傢伙報仇吧!
Comment: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爭取到的時間應該夠多了吧
Comment: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點遠離這個傢伙!
Comment: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不會吧... 為什麼?
Comment: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難不成...
Comment: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是艾連所在的位置...
Comment: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,感覺如何? 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的立體機動裝置呢
Comment: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事
Comment: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當時我將扣環鬆開了
Comment: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以沒有摔壞
Comment: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是嗎
Comment: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那就好
Comment: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是現在怎麼辦
Comment: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只剩下一匹馬而已
Comment: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果約翰的馬回來的話就能三人一起移動了
Comment: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他該死的 為什麼
Comment: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萊納的馬都已經回來了
Comment: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼我的馬死都不回來
Comment: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們明明就不能繼續停留在這裡...
Comment: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最糟的狀況有一人必須留下來...
Comment: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到時候那一個人要怎麼決定出來...
Comment: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是受傷的阿爾敏嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是身材高大兩個人騎會很擠的萊納嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是說我該用跑的去找自己的馬?
Comment: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡!
Comment: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真該死 為了這種事情煩惱
Comment: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們三個人好不容易才能死裡逃生
Comment: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣也未免太過份了吧
Comment: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然你的意識還不夠清楚嗎?
Comment: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯... 頭還是有點暈
Comment: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊...
Comment: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是該作出決定了
Comment: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然會是個殘酷的選擇
Comment: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來我們需要有一人留在這裡
Comment: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等等!
Comment: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這之前先發射信號彈看看
Comment: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果陣形還是直線前進的話
Comment: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,四列三班應該快到這附近了
Comment: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是緊急狀況用的信號彈
Comment: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然我覺得光靠這個應該無法傳達我們的意思
Comment: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:05:58.65,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們再等三分鐘
Comment: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在此之前我們必須作出誰留下來的決定
Comment: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:03.62,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,我留下來
Comment: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有件事情希望你們可以幫我代為報告
Comment: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最好能只向艾爾文團長報告就好
Comment: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等等 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那件事你自己去報告
Comment: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好像有人過來了
Comment: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且還帶了兩匹馬
Comment: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個是...
Comment: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,克里斯塔!
Comment: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家
Comment: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧?
Comment: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這不是我的馬嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好啦 好啦 冷靜點 普法洛特
Comment: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這孩子非常害怕地往我這邊逃來
Comment: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們跟巨人戰鬥了是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個傷是...
Comment: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要緊吧
Comment: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯 還可以
Comment: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒想到妳看到那信號彈後會想到要過來
Comment: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我正好在附近
Comment: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且約翰的馬也在我這裡
Comment: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬好像很喜歡妳
Comment: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來妳具備了某項不可思議的特質啊
Comment: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這下算是撿回一條命了
Comment: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是真的太好了
Comment: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們...
Comment: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能避開最糟糕的情況
Comment: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的是太好了
Comment: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是神啊...
Comment: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女神...
Comment: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好想跟她結婚...
Comment: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好了 我們要趕快歸隊
Comment: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,哦 對了
Comment: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該已經下達了撤退的命令
Comment: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過才走出城牆不到一小時就回頭
Comment: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來情況比想像中還要更灰黯
Comment: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且那傢伙還往指揮班相反的方向跑去
Comment: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙?
Comment: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然是綠色的信號彈
Comment: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來是只改變陣形的方向 繼續進行作戰的樣子
Comment: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼會...
Comment: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不是撤退命令嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文團長到底在想些什麼
Comment: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能判斷「作戰無法持續」的
Comment: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該是屬於全士兵們才對啊...
Comment: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道司令班下達的信號彈沒有傳達到?
Comment: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算不知道原因 以現在的情況我們該做的事情很明顯
Comment: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,遵從判斷
Comment: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,信號彈...
Comment: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是綠色的
Comment: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,歐魯
Comment: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,由你來發射
Comment: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解!
Comment: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然現在看起來很順暢地在前進
Comment: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但實際上的狀況又是如何
Comment: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最前面的應該已經有死傷了吧
Comment: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,報告!
Comment: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是口頭傳令! 右翼搜索部隊遭到毀滅性的攻擊!
Comment: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有一部分已經喪失搜索功能!
Comment: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以上內容請往左方繼續傳達下去!
Comment: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳聽見了嗎? 佩托拉
Comment: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去吧!
Comment: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,右翼?!
Comment: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我記得阿爾敏就在那裡...
Comment: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是阿爾敏跟其他人應該還留在中央附近待命才對
Comment: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還不致於遭到巨人的攻擊吧
Comment: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,黑色的信號彈!?
Comment: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是奇行種!?
Comment: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連由你來發射
Comment: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好!
Comment: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是什麼慘狀
Comment: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,居然已經深入到陣形之中
Comment: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人已經非常接近了
Comment: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在那信號彈的下方
Comment: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有人在戰鬥著...
Comment: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死的
Comment: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看這邊啊!
Comment: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳這個...
Comment: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怪物!
Comment: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是現在!
Comment: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,三個方向同時進攻
Comment: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然她看起來還挺聰明的
Comment: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但應該無法完全應付吧
Comment: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從脊椎到後腳跟哪裡都好
Comment: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要削掉就能阻止她
Comment: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上啊!
Comment: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然讓我們造成不必要的傷亡
Comment: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在老子就把妳給宰了
Comment: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跳起來了...
Comment: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快放開啊!
Comment: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,先回報再說...
Comment: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然有這種傢伙!
Comment: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不趕快通知其他人的話...
Comment: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是奇行種嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然來到這裡了
Comment: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,攔截她!
Comment: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不能再讓她繼續深入陣形了
Comment: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說右翼已經是全滅狀態?
Comment: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣還不撤退嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼?
Comment: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰知道
Comment: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是團長的指示
Comment: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之把命令向左翼傳達過去
Comment: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是怎麼一回事
Comment: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從剛才開始的行進方向就一直向東
Comment: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目的地舊市中心應該是在南方的啊
Comment: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再這樣下去陣形會撞上那裡
Comment: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊
Comment: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經可以看到了...
Comment: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那座巨木森林
Comment: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來有巨人經過的跡象
Comment: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,路上都沒有草木生長
Comment: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,載貨馬車應該可以通行
Comment: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,向後方傳達下去
Comment: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來只有中央的載貨馬車護衛班進入森林
Comment: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,遵命!
Comment: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個... 班長
Comment: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,中央列隊好像進入森林了...
Comment: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們繼續前進的話會碰上森林唷
Comment: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們繞路走
Comment: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂喂 幹嘛來這種觀光勝地
Comment: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無論是離本來的目的地還是折返點都偏離了很遠
Comment: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不清楚
Comment: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然不清楚
Comment: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但這是艾爾文團長的判斷
Comment: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想應該是有什麼打算才對
Comment: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那到底是什麼鬼打算
Comment: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,打算在觀光勝地舉辦我們新兵的歡迎典禮是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不... 我覺得沒這回事
Comment: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我開玩笑啦
Comment: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無論如何
Comment: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個巨大的女人追了過來
Comment: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不論是有什麼線索
Comment: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們也不能停留在這個地方
Comment: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「穿過這裡再往其他方向前進」除了這樣我想不到其它的了
Comment: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全員停下!
Comment: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好了 新兵們
Comment: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好好聽著
Comment: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來我們要進入迎敵隊形
Comment: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,拔劍後在樹上待命
Comment: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要有巨人打算進入森林就全力阻止!
Comment: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,呃... 那個班長...
Comment: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個是...
Comment: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,閉嘴遵命就是了
Comment: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真假啊
Comment: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底變成怎樣了
Comment: 0,0:14:58.13,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那...那個...
Comment: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好像只有中央列進入森林了
Comment: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不管陣形了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經沒有陣形可言了
Comment: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們左右的陣形遭受到森林阻攔
Comment: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只能從周邊繞道而行
Comment: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣就喪失搜索敵人的能力了
Comment: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼不改變路線避開這座森林呢?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是說艾爾文團長看錯地圖了?
Comment: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不清楚
Comment: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或許是為了躲避從右翼來的威脅
Comment: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,才會被迫逃進這裡
Comment: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也說不定
Comment: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,簡直是瘋了
Comment: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放棄當初打造後勤據點的作戰方式
Comment: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在那個時候我們就該夾著尾巴逃了才對
Comment: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是卻大膽繞道跑來這個觀光勝地...
Comment: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結果就只是這樣站著發呆
Comment: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,叫我阻止試圖進入森林的巨人
Comment: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙
Comment: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然下達如此荒唐的命令
Comment: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他會聽到的喔
Comment: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且連個像樣的說明都沒有 還真創新呢
Comment: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過我看他自己也很不安
Comment: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼說?
Comment: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在惡劣的狀況下被部屬判斷為無能的指揮官
Comment: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,經常因為背上出現不明傷痕而翹掉
Comment: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這種事情並不少見啊
Comment: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰...
Comment: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那你打算怎麼辦?
Comment: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別當真啊
Comment: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只是對這種狀況感到煩躁罷了
Comment: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真問我要怎麼做的話...
Comment: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當然是遵從命令
Comment: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不讓巨人進入森林
Comment: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你也認為應該要這麼做對吧?
Comment: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看你一副知道原因的樣子
Comment: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個...
Comment: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,五公尺級接近!!
Comment: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼要讓陣形往這個地方來?
Comment: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文團長到底在想什麼?
Comment: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...不對
Comment: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他在想的並不是這裡
Comment: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女巨人追著艾連
Comment: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後就是團長知道這件事情
Comment: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣子去假設並從這點去思考...
Comment: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長!
Comment: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里維士官長!
Comment: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼?
Comment: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還問我什麼事...
Comment: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡是森林欸
Comment: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果只有中央列進入森林的話
Comment: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有巨人接近也無法察覺啊!
Comment: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,似乎有東西從右翼接近
Comment: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們要如何閃躲巨人?
Comment: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又要如何去保護馬車呢?
Comment: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要因為這種淺顯易懂的問題自亂陣腳
Comment: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種事情早就辦不到了
Comment: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你仔細看看四周
Comment: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這些長得他媽高的巨木
Comment: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是讓我們能夠充分利用立體機動裝置的絕佳環境
Comment: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後你好好想想
Comment: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,用你那顆不怎麼靈光的腦袋
Comment: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不想死的話就動動腦袋
Comment: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我懂了...
Comment: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我只是菜鳥還不搞清楚現在的狀況
Comment: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他之所以不輕易告訴我答案
Comment: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是因為我必須自己去學習
Comment: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前輩們應該也是這樣從戰鬥中學習經驗的吧
Comment: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼跟什麼
Comment: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,簡直是胡鬧
Comment: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底是鬧三小
Comment: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底是怎樣啊
Comment: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是的
Comment: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難不成...
Comment: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道...
Comment: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡面沒人...
Comment: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒人能理解這個狀況嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該不會...
Comment: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就連里維士官長都...
Comment: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女巨人追著艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果這個假設成立
Comment: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來這裡的理由只有一個
Comment: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文團長想在這將女巨人給...
Comment: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,命令是說...
Comment: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要讓巨人進到森林裡面...
Comment: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對吧?
Comment: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說...
Comment: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有交戰的必要...
Comment: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對吧?
Comment: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,黑色信號彈
Comment: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從正後方傳來的!
Comment: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是從右翼來的那傢伙嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們幾個把劍拔出來!
Comment: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙一旦出現...
Comment: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,機會就只有一瞬間!
Comment: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快跑
Comment: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好快
Comment: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這森林裡根本無法事先迴避...
Comment: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會被追上的!
Comment: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長! 我們應該快點進入立體機動狀態!
Comment: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長!
Comment: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別想逃!
Comment: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從後方來了增援!
Comment: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長!
Comment: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,下命令啊!!
Comment: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們上吧!
Comment: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙太危險了!
Comment: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們應該出手了!
Comment: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓我來把她切成肉塊!
Comment: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,白痴...
Comment: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,自己要闖進地獄
Comment: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳追的可是專殺巨人的殺手集團啊!
Comment: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里維士官長?!
Comment: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長!
Comment: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請下達命令!
Comment: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再這樣下去會被追上
Comment: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們必須在這裡阻止她
Comment: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了這個我們才進入了森林
Comment: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是這樣對吧
Comment: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長!
Comment: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長 請下指示!
Comment: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全部人遮住耳朵
Comment: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,ed
Comment: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將人屠殺殆盡後追來的女巨人
Comment: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在夥伴於眼前被殺卻只能逃亡的情況之中
Comment: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連被逼迫於做出某項決定
